@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_jsarbm(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((tmp * (v1 + 0.77 + v1 + 0.85)) / (wp.abs(v0 + 0.34) * v1))
    v1 = (0.04 - ((tmp + 0.28 + v0 + 0.95) * wp.cos(tmp + 0.96)))
    tmp = wp.abs(0.29)
    v0 = wp.exp(v1)
    v0 = wp.sin(wp.abs((v2 + 0.10 * v1 + 0.21)))
    v2 = wp.cos((0.02 - wp.exp(v0 + 0.43)))
    data[tid] = v0
